OL,3,CC4 marketing of controversial
OL,4,Cprogramme purely about chasing ratings?
OL,6,GIt was the most talked about programme
OL,7,Gof the week ` or at least the one many
OL,8,Gnewspaper journalists devoted large
OL,9,Gamounts of space to.
OL,11,FGo Back to Where You Came From took a
OL,12,Fgroup who were hostile towards asylum
OL,13,Fseekers and attempted to show them
OL,14,Fjust what refugees were attempting to
OL,15,Fescape from.
OL,17,FTo say this programme has divided
OL,18,Fopinion would be an understatement.
OL,20,FTo critics, it is simply irresponsible
OL,21,Fand even dangerous ` a platform for
OL,22,Fsome with highly offensive views.
