OL,3,CC4 marketing of controversial
OL,4,Cprogramme purely about chasing ratings?
OL,6,FAnnouncers and promotions need to be
OL,7,Fabout more than marketing when they
OL,8,Fare dealing with disturbing and
OL,9,Fcontroversial content.
OL,11,FSimilarly, if part of the point of
OL,12,Fthis programme is to provoke debate
OL,13,Fthen the channel should find a forum
OL,14,Ffor the discussion.
OL,16,FFor many years C4 did just that. Right
OL,17,Fto Reply and The Television Show were
OL,18,Fdesigned to give viewers a chance to
OL,19,Fdebate and discuss the substance of
OL,20,Fprogrammes and creative decisions.
