OL,3,CC4 marketing of controversial
OL,4,Cprogramme purely about chasing ratings?
OL,6,FWorse, modern C4 often seems just like
OL,7,Fany other commercial channel.
OL,9,FSo it is easy to imagine that all its
OL,10,Foutput is simply designed to maximise
OL,11,Fratings and get the best possible
OL,12,Freturn.
OL,14,FWhen privatisation seemed likely, I
OL,15,Fdiscussed how relatively little of
OL,16,Fmodern C4 is truly distinctive ` much
OL,17,Fcan either seem mainstream, derivative
OL,18,For simply puerile.
OL,20,FThis can make it harder to spot when a
OL,21,Fprogramme aspires to some other
OL,22,Fpurpose.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/8
